 Da, da.

184
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:30,500
 Jesam u Pravom.

185
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:31,500
 Je, je, da.

186
00:15:31,500 --> 00:15:32,500
 Zadnja prije Kaveza.

187
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:33,500
 Da, da.

188
