00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:10,500
 To su sve ljudi koji, koji, ono, životno, životno...

196
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:11,500
 I legendarni Mario Tušek.

197
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:13,500
 I legendarni Mario Tušek, moj kum.

198
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:14,500
 Naš ninja.

199
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:15,500
 Tako je.

200
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,500
 On mi je isto...

201
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,500
 Mario.

202
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:20,500
 Mislim da su oni...

203
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:22,500
 A mi si sam ono od boraca kušil.

204
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:24,500
 Od boraca, da.

205
